Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你在哪裏?天野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根羽毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后,請別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根羽毛,感覺好像很哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撞到地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走這條航道似乎有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們飛高點走別的路線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白這樣會有多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但唯有這條路才能不被\N寨巴哈發現,安全抵達弗雷特公國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也唯有你們才辦得到,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成功越過這座山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓寨巴哈大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你也會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在弗雷特等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要阻止我也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要捨棄國家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憊你一個人,明明什麼都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再把我當孩子看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還有父王總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不考量我的心情,就擅自為我下決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是為了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我放棄繼續學醫也是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王族學習醫術有什麼用?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想做些能夠幫助其他人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為王族只要在其位為民盡其本分就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任意妄為才是對人民的褻瀆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡亞連!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神人乃背上長有翅膀之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯的末裔遭到詛咒的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神人?絕對不能接近龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近龍神人者必死無疑,帶來世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅了亞特蘭提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您別這樣,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梵大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,好危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你一直說想看的耶,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,還是太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了,你好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利之後的酒果然特別好暍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這個小隊一定會率先攻入敵人主力陣營
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法尼利亞的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾卡斯\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭結束以後,你就要離開了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下想要重新鍛煉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這份恩情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,巴爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能繼續精進武士之道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠再回到我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回到法尼利亞來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下,這裏很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,巴爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是魔人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我被那樣的魔人奪去性命都無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是法尼利亞的鞏恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會曉得我的名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚,當幻之月升至西山頂時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的男人將會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我出生時的占卜預言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命中注定的相會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭莉葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭莉葉,你願意跟我走嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,鞏恩大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梵的爸爸跟媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能迎娶龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神人是使亞特蘭提斯滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到詛咒的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會為法尼利亞招來禍患
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不同意這樁婚姻,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論傳說為何,這都與芭莉葉無關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都無法拆散我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當有精神的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的弟弟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王,他叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵·法尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你不能讓人見到你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在時候來臨前,你絕對不能將你的翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應母后,別讓母后難過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是沒能趕上…鞏恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會代替王兄成為國王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為像父王一樣的堅強男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請您別再哭了,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒多久後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后隻身一人循著王兄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯的步伐走進了森林中的龍巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾卡斯曾經進入森林裏幫我去找尋過母后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻毫無所獲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后再也沒有回到城裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這些事告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的翅膀…我很喜歡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜歡,很漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有你和梅露露會說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我跟梅露露一樣笨嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的預見是一片渾沌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉沒於混亂的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不讓我看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍影覆蓋了未來的預見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,我們接下來要去哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得弗雷特公國應該就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說不上來,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈的那些隱形傢伙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏…他們的確就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,梅露露,你們抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射得太偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已經瞄準了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方似乎可以看見我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不讓他死就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會從哪裏攻擊過來?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用跑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,梅露露,你們下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了,快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林凡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水中就算隱形也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能看得到你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你看不看得見,結果都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接把你給毀了如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍擊隊成功捕獲目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將龍回收
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來人救救梵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵啊,這就是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方出現浮遊船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興能夠再見到你,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你這混帳,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蓋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太大意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你回答我啊,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公國的商船隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒退,迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特的船正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在讓他們看到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰計劃就會被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打得正順呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回答我啊,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法止血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有醫生在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船隻是往來於阿斯多利亞的"蘭潘德"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與弗雷特的"戈達西姆"之間的貿易船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上並沒有能夠醫治這種重傷的醫生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了要救我,才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是迦迪斯的聲音,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰受傷了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷勢…出血這麼嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,你還在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點幫他治療啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去亞連會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我找不到醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,你應該行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經學習過醫術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只讀過書本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不曾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望亞連隊長活下去,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鼠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你將我的藍色包包拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老大有事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會馬上宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想麻醉應該生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你還是押住他,讓他不要掙扎亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您一定,一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救救亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾經打從心底信賴過某個人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛國者?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍瞳的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:05.52,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:13.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
